PURPOSE

The purpose of this Standard Operating Procedure (SOP) is to
establish a consistent and effective approach for performing data
backup and recovery at Tech Guard Solutions. This SOP aims to
safeguard critical data, ensure business continuity, and minimize
data loss in case of an unexpected event.

INTRODUCTION

Data backup and recovery are crucial components of our IT
infrastructure management. This SOP outlines the processes and
procedures to be followed to ensure that data is backed up
regularly, stored securely, and can be recovered quickly in the
event of data loss, system failure, or cyber-attack.

SCOPE

This SOP applies to all employees, contractors, and third-party
users at Tech Guard Solutions who are involved in data backup and
recovery processes. It covers all company-owned and managed
systems, databases, and applications that store or process critical
business data.

CHANGE HISTORY

Regular revisions should be conducted every two years to ensure the SOP remains current and effective.

